          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/908.-step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, shred the <strong>little gem</strong>&nbsp;<strong>lettuce</strong></p>\r\n<p>Peel and slice the <strong>shallot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/908.-step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/908.-step-5-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/908.-step-5-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/908.-step-5-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/908.-step-5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>mayonnaise</strong>&nbsp;and <strong>harissa paste&nbsp;</strong>(Can't handle the heat? Go easy!)&nbsp;in a bowl</p>\r\n<p>Add a drizzle of&nbsp;<strong>olive oil</strong> and mix well &ndash; this is your <strong>harissa mayo</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
